text: The following lists events that happened in 1909 in Iceland. ==Incumbents== *Prime Minister - Hannes Hafstein, Björn Jónsson ==Events== ==Births== *15 April - Friðjón Skarphéðinsson, politician (d. 1996). *15 May - Ingólfur Jónsson, politician (d. 1984). *17 July - Guðmundur Ívarsson Guðmundsson, politician (d. 1987) *18 November - Svavar Guðnason, painter (d. 1988) ==Deaths== ==References== Iceland Iceland Category:Years of the 20th century in Iceland
